# Web3Forms access key — delivers the contact form to the address the key is
# registered to. Free key from https://web3forms.com
#
# Public by design (Web3Forms keys are meant to be embedded client-side, and
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ inlines this into the browser bundle). It lives here so it stays
# out of the repo and can be rotated without a commit.
#
# The site is fully static, so this is baked in at BUILD time — changing it in
# Vercel requires a redeploy to take effect.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
